a:3:{s:5:"title";s:8:"Recycler";s:17:"short_description";s:45:"Restore or permanently remove deleted records";s:11:"description";s:261:"Allows you to restore deleted records or remove them permanently from the database. Supports single, multiple, and recursive actions, such as restoring a page with all its content elements. Filter by page or table to review deleted records before taking action.";}